Social media users have welcomed Julius Malema's call for Cape Town International Airport to be renamed Winnie Mandela Airport. JOHANNESBURG - Economic Freedom Fighters Julius Malema has called on the ANC to rename Cape Town International Airport to Winnie Mandela Airport. Malema made this pronouncement during his fiery speech at Winnie Madikizela-Mandela. Social media users responded with a resounding yes! Checkout some of the responses below:    